intro: You heard the knock. Now run.
description: TUNG TUNG SAHUR: The Backroom Drummer Straight out of your For You Page and into your nightmares. He’s wooden. He’s weird. He’s got a bat. And if you don’t answer when he calls… TUNG TUNG TUNG SAHUR, you're done. Dive into the chaos of the newest TikTok-core horror meme. Run, hide, or meme your way out of a surreal world filled with talking furniture, broken AI narrators, and a cursed wooden entity that's more viral than he is polite. There’s no tradition here—just loud banging, bad decisions, and backroom-level madness. Inspired by the weird side of the internet. No context. No rules. Just TUNG TUNG.
